snippet.title: Taxi Rush - Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist:
Steam Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2613400/Taxi_Rush/

Get behind the wheel in Taxi Rush and transport your passengers in this crazy big city! As a crazy taxi driver, get your passengers where they need to go on time. Traffic? Traffic Rules? Police? Red Lights? No, no, no, no, no, no. You're a crazy, lawless driver. Jump with your car if you have to!
